title: #92Noon! JG/Birk&Siny/Bercich/Lavelle/PJ
description: Full Monday show! Montage for the open with Vikings losing to Bears, JG on the Gophers, Matt Birk & Dave Sinykin combo to finish the first hour, Bercich midway thru with Vikings analysis, Lavelle in the mix during final hour, and then PJ Fleck wraps the show!
